headline: Is Smurfit Westrock a Bargain After Recent Share Recovery in 2025?
summary: If you’re staring at Smurfit Westrock stock and wondering whether now is the time to make a move, you’re in good company. The packaging giant has been on a bit of a journey, one that should catch the eye of any investor who likes to dig deeper than just the headlines. Over the past week, Smurfit Westrock shares have nudged up by 2.0%, with a similar 2.2% gain over the last month.
